            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Una forma de repetir líneas de código es escribirlas una y otra vez, pero lleva mucho tiempo si queremos crear programas más grandes.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"83\" /><option startIndex=\"83\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"93\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"</code> seguido de <code>and again</code> y finalmente <code>\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
